sent.orig: The discovery rate for wildcat wells in the Denver basin has changed radically with time.
sent.trans: 丹佛盆地的探井发现率随时间变化得很快。

sent.orig: Children under 12 years old the same with parents, without extra bed are of charge.
sent.trans: 儿童十二岁以下与父母同房不需加床，不另收费。

sent.orig: The solution that the Volvo engineers came up with was WHIPS (Whiplash Protection System).
sent.trans: Volvo工程师所提出的解决方案是whips（头颈部保护系统）。

sent.orig: May God strengthen our hands for the good work ahead-and always, always bless our America.
sent.trans: 愿上帝给我们强有力的双手，做好未来的工作——并且，永远，永远保佑我们美国。

sent.orig: He disappointeth the devices of the crafty, so that their hands cannot perform their enterprise.
sent.trans: 12破坏狡猾人的计谋，使他们所谋的不得成就。
